Speedbreaker and Wildrider both smirk as they follow Cyclonus in, "Oh boy,
I love playing the game when we got more players" Wildrider squeaks to
himself. As they enter the control room the message board has lit up. "This
is Motormaster, come in" booms his voice over the comm-link.
